WEBVTT

01:37.850 --> 01:41.039
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.090 --> 01:43.950
[Episode 31]

01:48.310 --> 01:50.070
I've actually imagined many times

01:50.070 --> 01:51.789
what it would be like for us
to be together.

01:51.789 --> 01:53.870
I could talk about art with you,

01:54.560 --> 01:56.640
take you to see exhibitions
all over the world

01:56.640 --> 01:58.500
and give you everything you want.

01:58.850 --> 01:59.759
You'll just need to stay

01:59.759 --> 02:01.090
by my side with no worry.

02:02.240 --> 02:03.040
So, Miyu,

02:04.260 --> 02:05.590
can you give me a chance?

02:20.360 --> 02:21.540
I'm sorry, Mr. Tan.

02:22.800 --> 02:25.130
I cannot accept your pursuit.

02:27.870 --> 02:29.650
Do you have someone you like?

02:34.920 --> 02:36.800
Alright. I got it.

02:37.970 --> 02:39.970
When we spent time together before,

02:40.620 --> 02:42.480
I didn't keep proper boundaries.

02:42.820 --> 02:45.250
I've always said we're friends,

02:45.310 --> 02:46.030
but

02:47.380 --> 02:48.780
actually, I've used you.

02:49.870 --> 02:53.320
To some degree, I've never
been completely honest with you.

02:54.400 --> 02:55.120
I'm sorry.

02:57.310 --> 02:59.180
Actually, you don't need to feel guilty.

02:59.180 --> 03:01.040
Wasn't I also just playing along?

03:01.850 --> 03:02.730
We're even now.

03:03.410 --> 03:03.970
Cheers.

03:12.310 --> 03:14.240
But we can still be friends, right?

03:14.270 --> 03:15.060
Of course.

03:15.590 --> 03:16.590
That's good then.

03:16.990 --> 03:17.829
Let's eat.

03:46.390 --> 03:47.910
-I'm sorry.
-You're here.

03:48.590 --> 03:50.260
I'm late because I overslept.

03:52.280 --> 03:54.410
You guys are doing pretty well.

03:54.880 --> 03:55.800
Is that steamer of food ready?

03:55.800 --> 03:58.220
Bring it over here for Chef Jiao
to take a look.

03:58.220 --> 04:00.680
I created a new dish today.

04:00.700 --> 04:01.650
Please taste it.

04:08.130 --> 04:09.100
This one.

04:23.830 --> 04:26.060
[Position and Employment Term]
[Employment Term: 3 Months]

04:23.950 --> 04:25.940
The contract is for 3 months.

04:26.370 --> 04:27.840
Then what will happen
after these 3 months?

04:27.840 --> 04:29.160
By that time,

04:29.180 --> 04:32.580
it depends on whether the hotel
wants to renew your contract.

04:33.260 --> 04:35.190
Why didn't I think of this earlier?

04:35.310 --> 04:37.310
Just like the beans
spilled from a bamboo tube,

04:37.310 --> 04:38.800
I held nothing back.

04:38.890 --> 04:40.950
I haven't even been paid for 2 months,

04:41.159 --> 04:42.670
and my apprentice
is already fully trained.

04:42.670 --> 04:43.540
What should I do?

04:43.540 --> 04:44.560
What can you do?

04:44.840 --> 04:46.540
If the hotel
doesn't want to renew your contract,

04:46.540 --> 04:47.890
then you'll just have to go home.

04:47.890 --> 04:49.159
Are you kidding me?

04:49.180 --> 04:51.690
My unique skill
is only worth tens of thousands of yuan?

04:51.690 --> 04:53.890
This is not okay. I have to call your dad.

04:54.730 --> 04:55.840
Gosh.

04:59.220 --> 05:00.240
Welcome.

05:00.260 --> 05:01.540
Welcome.

05:11.560 --> 05:12.590
Hello, sir.

05:12.620 --> 05:14.350
You can check in at the counter.

05:15.160 --> 05:17.540
I-I'm here to find...

05:17.670 --> 05:18.470
Xu...

05:21.640 --> 05:22.700
Xu Miyu.

05:22.800 --> 05:23.680
Okay.

05:28.910 --> 05:29.710
Miyu.

05:30.310 --> 05:30.950
Miyu.

05:30.970 --> 05:32.170
Please wait a moment.

05:35.490 --> 05:36.090
It's done.

05:36.100 --> 05:36.810
Thank you.

05:39.310 --> 05:39.740
Dad.

05:39.800 --> 05:40.250
You're busy, huh?

05:40.250 --> 05:41.210
When did you arrive?

05:41.210 --> 05:42.640
I just got here.

05:43.970 --> 05:44.880
Well,

05:45.120 --> 05:47.970
I don't even know where to start.

05:48.640 --> 05:51.280
Last time, I was just too angry

05:51.310 --> 05:52.800
and took it all out on you.

05:52.820 --> 05:53.970
It was my fault.

05:54.000 --> 05:54.680
D-Don't...

05:54.710 --> 05:57.020
It's okay. Dad, don't mention it anymore.

05:57.020 --> 05:58.150
It's all in the past.

05:58.630 --> 05:59.800
Okay. I won't mention it again.

05:59.800 --> 06:00.930
It's all in the past.

06:02.010 --> 06:04.330
I've heard you're doing well at the hotel.

06:04.330 --> 06:05.790
You're even a manager now.

06:06.820 --> 06:08.910
That's great. I'm happy for you.

06:10.230 --> 06:11.990
As for your live stream,

06:12.400 --> 06:14.490
wow, all the neighbors watched it.

06:14.520 --> 06:16.460
They all said you looked even prettier
and more elegant

06:16.460 --> 06:17.790
than those superstars.

06:19.410 --> 06:21.870
I knew you would be successful.

06:22.450 --> 06:24.780
You've really won honor for our Xu family.

06:26.230 --> 06:27.960
You're much better than Miyao.

06:28.490 --> 06:30.050
Ms. Xu! Ms. Xu!

06:30.190 --> 06:31.720
The switchboard room
needs you for a moment.

06:31.720 --> 06:33.450
Copy that. I'll be right there.

06:33.450 --> 06:35.730
Dad, go wait in Mom's room first.

06:35.750 --> 06:37.550
I've already booked a table for you
at the Chinese restaurant.

06:37.550 --> 06:39.080
Just mention my name later.

06:39.159 --> 06:39.620
Come on.

06:39.620 --> 06:39.840
Okay.

06:39.840 --> 06:40.520
Follow me.

06:41.870 --> 06:42.200
Well,

06:42.220 --> 06:43.510
let... let me carry this.

06:43.510 --> 06:44.460
-It's okay.
-It's quite heavy.

06:44.460 --> 06:45.020
Let me carry it.

06:45.020 --> 06:47.710
You have something else to do.
Give it to me first.

06:47.710 --> 06:48.600
Let me carry it.

06:51.540 --> 06:53.890
Why didn't you stop your dad
from coming here?

06:53.890 --> 06:55.159
Aren't you afraid the two of them

06:55.159 --> 06:56.820
will stop Mr. Ji at the office door

06:56.820 --> 06:58.280
and just ask him for money?

06:58.380 --> 07:01.470
I know, but he's my dad after all.

07:01.500 --> 07:03.780
What's more, he said my mom's contract
would expire soon,

07:03.780 --> 07:05.050
so he wanted to come and pick her up.

07:05.050 --> 07:06.660
He also said
he wanted to take this chance to visit me.

07:06.660 --> 07:07.980
How could I refuse?

07:08.190 --> 07:10.570
Anyway, judging by this situation,
it's definitely nothing good.

07:10.570 --> 07:11.880
You have to be careful.

07:13.720 --> 07:14.600
Qiaoqi.

07:15.080 --> 07:16.120
Just take them.

07:16.210 --> 07:17.090
Thanks.

07:26.930 --> 07:28.930
I thought about it carefully later.

07:29.430 --> 07:31.130
What you said makes sense.

07:31.750 --> 07:32.870
All these clauses

07:32.900 --> 07:34.530
were written by lawyers.

07:34.560 --> 07:36.820
There are no loopholes we can make use of.

07:41.950 --> 07:43.080
I should be content.

07:44.010 --> 07:46.400
Having worked as a chef in such a

07:46.430 --> 07:47.670
five-star hotel,

07:48.310 --> 07:49.310
I'll have much

07:49.350 --> 07:51.350
to brag about for the rest of my life.

07:51.740 --> 07:53.620
Come on.
Let's drink a toast to our teacher.

07:53.620 --> 07:57.590
-Thank you! Cheers!
-Cheers!

08:12.210 --> 08:14.130
This portion of boat pastries
is called Qinhuai Lifestyle.

08:14.130 --> 08:14.940
Please enjoy.

08:18.920 --> 08:20.700
This is created by my apprentice,

08:20.700 --> 08:21.900
Chef Bao.

08:22.160 --> 08:23.180
I've tasted it.

08:23.210 --> 08:24.470
It's quite delicious.

08:24.550 --> 08:26.480
Taste this to see how it is.

08:28.600 --> 08:32.000
What kind of nonsense
have you been blabbering about?

08:35.600 --> 08:37.690
What did I say wrong again?

08:40.030 --> 08:41.870
"Teach the apprentice, starve the master."

08:41.870 --> 08:43.600
Don't you know this old saying?

08:44.520 --> 08:46.630
You're stupid and undereducated.

08:47.830 --> 08:49.070
What should I do then?

08:50.580 --> 08:54.060
I'm here to get justice for you.

08:56.050 --> 08:57.630
None of them can take your cooking skills

08:57.630 --> 08:58.510
lightly.

09:15.060 --> 09:15.780
Ms. Xu.

09:19.870 --> 09:21.470
Are you looking for someone?

09:21.640 --> 09:23.170
I'm looking for my parents.

09:23.310 --> 09:24.320
I've just promised them

09:24.320 --> 09:26.100
I'll take them out for a walk after work.

09:26.100 --> 09:27.450
But they're not in their room.

09:27.450 --> 09:29.750
I thought they came to the lobby
to wait for me.

09:29.750 --> 09:30.770
They haven't been here.

09:30.770 --> 09:32.630
There aren't many people
in the lobby this morning,

09:32.630 --> 09:33.800
and I've been here the whole time.

09:33.800 --> 09:34.580
If they had come,

09:34.580 --> 09:36.240
I would definitely remember.

09:36.800 --> 09:38.310
Where are they?

09:38.660 --> 09:39.730
They're not in the restaurant, either.

09:39.730 --> 09:41.580
Nor did they reply to my WeChat messages.

09:41.580 --> 09:43.930
Where... Where are they?

09:47.730 --> 09:57.320
[Purong Hotel]

09:47.890 --> 09:50.560
Mr. Ji, regarding my skills,

09:50.630 --> 09:54.030
if you take them away just like that...

09:55.550 --> 09:57.480
We agreed to properly thank Mr. Ji

09:57.480 --> 09:59.390
before we leave.

09:59.660 --> 10:01.670
What nonsense are you talking about now?

10:01.670 --> 10:03.550
Didn't you tell me to say...

10:03.780 --> 10:04.540
I...

10:04.980 --> 10:07.470
What did I tell you to say?

10:07.750 --> 10:10.600
You've been chattering to me
in the past few days,

10:10.620 --> 10:12.840
saying how well
the boat pastries are selling,

10:12.840 --> 10:14.670
and that what you've contributed
isn't physical labor

10:14.670 --> 10:16.260
but an intangible cultural heritage skill.

10:16.260 --> 10:18.010
I only asked her this one question.

10:18.010 --> 10:20.010
I said, "Isn't your hotel's revenue

10:20.210 --> 10:22.660
connected to the employees' performance?"

10:22.660 --> 10:24.850
Didn't I only ask you this one question?

10:24.850 --> 10:25.800
And what are you doing now?

10:25.800 --> 10:27.920
You're here asking for money.

10:28.070 --> 10:30.230
I don't know.

10:31.010 --> 10:33.010
I think I understand what you mean.

10:34.750 --> 10:37.320
Chef Jiao's boat pastries
became a smash hit,

10:37.340 --> 10:40.630
directly contributing to half the success
of our F&B Department.

10:40.630 --> 10:42.630
Although our hotel generously offered

10:42.630 --> 10:44.000
the highest pay in the market to hire her,

10:44.000 --> 10:45.860
Chef Jiao is still not satisfied.

10:45.880 --> 10:46.510
Right?

10:46.610 --> 10:47.530
Yes, yes, yes.

10:47.670 --> 10:48.930
That's exactly what I mean.

10:48.930 --> 10:49.690
Look.

10:49.900 --> 10:51.950
Mr. Ji is a perceptive man.

10:53.660 --> 10:54.500
Mr. Ji,

10:54.520 --> 10:56.920
please don't blame me
for talking too much.

10:57.540 --> 10:59.320
Regarding the pay offered to hire her,

10:59.320 --> 11:01.420
the hotel has indeed been generous enough.

11:01.420 --> 11:02.670
We've witnessed it

11:02.670 --> 11:03.730
and kept it in mind.

11:04.150 --> 11:06.690
But after the success
of the boat pastries,

11:06.720 --> 11:09.480
the hotel hasn't shown any appreciation,

11:09.760 --> 11:13.290
which definitely hurts our feelings a bit.

11:13.510 --> 11:15.280
-We just feel...
-I feel quite upset.

11:15.280 --> 11:17.870
It feels like you'll get rid of us
once you've finished using us.

11:17.870 --> 11:18.680
Right?

11:21.740 --> 11:28.070
[Purong Hotel]

11:22.830 --> 11:25.080
Look. We've contributed

11:25.110 --> 11:26.510
the cooking skills.

11:26.900 --> 11:28.310
The employment term
will also be over soon.

11:28.310 --> 11:30.390
Then we'll just take
tens of thousands of yuan

11:30.390 --> 11:31.240
of employment fees

11:31.240 --> 11:33.390
and leave with nothing else, huh?

11:33.550 --> 11:35.910
So what is the price in your mind?

11:37.480 --> 11:38.320
100,000 yuan.

11:40.650 --> 11:41.490
200,000 yuan.

11:47.910 --> 11:50.030
With the revenue brought by
Chef Jiao's afternoon tea snacks,

11:50.030 --> 11:51.370
according to the regulations,

11:51.370 --> 11:52.730
if it's converted into a bonus,

11:52.730 --> 11:54.680
the hotel can offer 150,000 yuan.

11:55.790 --> 11:58.790
The remaining 50,000 yuan
will be considered as my personal

11:58.790 --> 12:00.970
gratitude to Chef Jiao
for her valuable guidance.

12:00.970 --> 12:02.100
200,000 yuan, deal.

12:05.030 --> 12:06.390
But I have a condition.

12:07.330 --> 12:08.570
Go ahead.

12:13.890 --> 12:14.640
What?

12:15.510 --> 12:17.080
We need to use this 200,000 yuan

12:17.080 --> 12:18.890
to pay off my daughter's debt?

12:18.990 --> 12:19.790
That's right.

12:20.190 --> 12:20.920
Mr. Ji,

12:20.950 --> 12:22.730
I-I understand what you mean.

12:23.790 --> 12:26.630
You've helped us arrange the use
of this money in advance.

12:26.630 --> 12:27.510
However,

12:28.600 --> 12:31.100
as they say,
every family has its own problems.

12:31.100 --> 12:33.000
T-This debt is

12:33.000 --> 12:35.200
our family's private matter after all.

12:35.390 --> 12:37.440
As for who will pay the debt,

12:37.440 --> 12:39.190
how we'll pay it
and how much should be paid,

12:39.190 --> 12:41.390
you really don't need to worry about it.

12:41.560 --> 12:43.320
But these personal debts

12:43.340 --> 12:44.190
have affected

12:44.250 --> 12:46.510
our hotel employee's work performance.

12:46.570 --> 12:48.000
She's always worried,

12:48.000 --> 12:49.480
being unable to focus on work,

12:49.480 --> 12:51.860
which has affected
our hotel's performance and revenue.

12:51.860 --> 12:53.420
If I don't care, who will?

12:53.450 --> 12:55.110
Don't worry about that, Mr. Ji.

12:55.110 --> 12:57.480
I know my daughter's personality
perfectly well.

12:57.480 --> 12:59.010
Even if the sky were to fall,

12:59.080 --> 13:01.370
I'm sure she would still work earnestly.

13:01.390 --> 13:02.650
So you just think it's completely fine

13:02.650 --> 13:04.110
to throw the burden on her?

13:04.550 --> 13:05.550
Do you know

13:05.800 --> 13:06.870
she used her own credit

13:06.870 --> 13:08.070
to guarantee for you?

13:08.120 --> 13:09.410
Due to her trust in you,

13:09.510 --> 13:10.870
she made the sacrifice.

13:12.410 --> 13:15.160
Mr. Ji, we country folks
don't know how to talk properly.

13:15.160 --> 13:16.510
But please rest assured.

13:16.510 --> 13:17.630
She's our own daughter,

13:17.630 --> 13:19.080
and we know her well.

13:19.400 --> 13:21.560
She has the ability to pay off this debt.

13:21.560 --> 13:23.020
After all, when she borrowed the money,

13:23.020 --> 13:24.870
she was still a rich man's wife,
wasn't she?

13:24.870 --> 13:26.380
But she isn't anymore.

13:26.410 --> 13:28.020
Since she has moved on,

13:28.180 --> 13:30.510
why are you two
still stuck in an illusion?

13:32.520 --> 13:33.810
W-We...

13:55.220 --> 13:57.130
Today is a great day.

13:57.370 --> 13:58.730
The three of us

13:58.760 --> 14:00.170
should celebrate properly.

14:00.170 --> 14:00.720
Come on. Cheers.

14:00.720 --> 14:01.160
Cheers.

14:01.160 --> 14:01.690
Cheers.

14:01.980 --> 14:02.550
Cheers!

14:02.580 --> 14:03.390
Let's drink a toast.

14:03.390 --> 14:03.970
Cheers.

14:05.010 --> 14:06.410
What are we celebrating?

14:06.480 --> 14:10.940
We're celebrating your mom's successful
completion of her job at Purong Hotel.

14:11.670 --> 14:14.170
Alright. Let me tell you.
I've thought it over.

14:14.170 --> 14:16.410
While the boat pastries are still popular,

14:16.410 --> 14:19.200
let's hurry back to the guesthouse
and do some marketing, too.

14:19.200 --> 14:21.410
Firstly, we can set up a decorative wall

14:21.440 --> 14:22.720
and cover it with photos.

14:22.720 --> 14:24.310
What kind of photos?

14:24.340 --> 14:26.740
Your work photos at the hotel.

14:26.770 --> 14:28.670
Your photos
with the hotel management staff.

14:28.670 --> 14:29.600
And previously,

14:29.840 --> 14:31.910
weren't there some large-scale events
in your hotel?

14:31.910 --> 14:33.210
Didn't you take photos with those VIPs

14:33.210 --> 14:34.770
and guests?

14:34.800 --> 14:36.440
Wouldn't that be too vulgar?

14:37.010 --> 14:38.250
Don't worry.

14:38.270 --> 14:39.970
The vulgarest things
are the most effective.

14:39.970 --> 14:41.850
Right? Guests just like that.

14:42.470 --> 14:43.270
Oh, by the way.

14:43.290 --> 14:45.330
when we get back there,
I also need to see Li first.

14:45.330 --> 14:46.470
Isn't his son running

14:46.470 --> 14:48.330
a matchmaking agency in our town?

14:48.390 --> 14:49.480
We'll pay him some money

14:49.480 --> 14:52.180
and ask him
to shoot a good promo video for you.

14:52.400 --> 14:54.940
We'll just play it on a loop
in the guesthouse restaurant

14:54.940 --> 14:56.090
to promote our place properly.

14:56.090 --> 14:57.630
That's a great idea. I like it.

14:57.630 --> 14:58.210
Okay.

14:59.150 --> 15:00.700
Dad, Mom.

15:02.220 --> 15:05.880
There's still a network loan
of over 200,000 yuan for me to pay off.

15:07.480 --> 15:09.900
Don't you have to pay
only 5,000 yuan a month?

15:09.900 --> 15:12.420
Only 5,000 yuan? Will you pay the money?

15:12.750 --> 15:13.630
Of course.

15:14.630 --> 15:16.370
If we have the money,
we'll definitely pay.

15:16.370 --> 15:17.730
Then pay the debt now.

15:17.750 --> 15:19.150
Don't you have money now?

15:20.840 --> 15:23.910
-What... What money?
-You asked Mr. Ji for 200,000 yuan.

15:23.910 --> 15:24.970
I know everything.

15:27.420 --> 15:31.130
That sum of money is another matter.

15:32.370 --> 15:34.090
You know what? Now we've met another...

15:34.090 --> 15:35.890
Just treat me as a nuisance, too.

15:38.010 --> 15:40.470
Consider that 200,000 yuan
as my hush money.

15:41.440 --> 15:43.640
I'll figure out a way to pay off the rest.

15:44.240 --> 15:46.340
In the future, I won't ask you two
for money anymore.

15:46.340 --> 15:47.980
This network loan of over 300,000 yuan

15:47.980 --> 15:49.730
can be paid off with just 200,000 yuan.

15:49.730 --> 15:51.700
You can even make a net profit
of 100,000 yuan.

15:51.700 --> 15:52.780
It's such a good deal, isn't it?

15:52.780 --> 15:55.440
W-What are you talking about?

15:55.900 --> 15:57.940
Why do you sound so distant?

15:58.000 --> 16:00.990
It sounds as if you were trying to
distance yourself from us.

16:00.990 --> 16:02.320
Hearing you say that,

16:02.340 --> 16:04.080
I feel a bit hurt.

16:04.150 --> 16:05.570
Don't make such jokes anymore.

16:05.570 --> 16:06.900
I'm not joking with you.

16:07.630 --> 16:09.160
This 200,000 yuan is yours.

16:10.250 --> 16:11.750
The network loan of over 300,000 yuan
I've borrowed

16:11.750 --> 16:12.630
is also yours.

16:13.240 --> 16:14.730
Even I am yours.

16:15.810 --> 16:16.650
Does it matter

16:17.710 --> 16:19.190
who I am?

16:19.750 --> 16:21.030
When I had the ability,

16:21.030 --> 16:22.630
I helped you two build a guesthouse

16:22.630 --> 16:23.680
and pay the network loan.

16:23.680 --> 16:26.330
After I lost that ability,
I have to make a living myself

16:26.330 --> 16:27.530
and survive on my own.

16:27.830 --> 16:29.640
Dad, Mom.

16:30.520 --> 16:32.120
When you were using me,

16:32.140 --> 16:34.000
had you ever loved me for a moment?

16:34.270 --> 16:35.390
Miyu,

16:35.640 --> 16:38.020
what you said isn't nice.

16:38.120 --> 16:39.120
No matter what,

16:39.270 --> 16:40.810
we've brought you up after all, right?

16:40.810 --> 16:41.220
Yes.

16:42.180 --> 16:43.640
You've been telling me you brought me up

16:43.640 --> 16:45.500
for as many years as you raised me.

16:46.590 --> 16:47.750
I was just too grateful

16:47.750 --> 16:49.030
and felt too guilty,

16:49.370 --> 16:51.320
so I tried so hard to leave the village

16:51.320 --> 16:52.870
and marry into the city

16:53.390 --> 16:55.440
to repay your kindness.

16:56.150 --> 16:57.080
Only until now have I realized

16:57.080 --> 16:57.960
I was so stupid.

16:58.670 --> 17:00.190
All you want is money.

17:00.790 --> 17:01.910
Gratitude and guilt

17:01.910 --> 17:03.750
were the password
you used to withdraw money

17:03.750 --> 17:05.280
from me, who was like an ATM.

17:06.069 --> 17:06.829
From today onwards,

17:06.829 --> 17:08.270
this password is cancelled.

17:08.270 --> 17:09.750
From now on,
if it's about money, we discuss money,

17:09.750 --> 17:11.950
and if it's about matters,
we discuss matters.

17:11.950 --> 17:13.750
This way, it's easier for us all.

17:13.760 --> 17:14.480
Miyu,

17:14.480 --> 17:16.000
aren't you my daughter?

17:16.000 --> 17:17.020
Yes, I am.

17:17.270 --> 17:19.079
Of course I am your daughter.

17:19.530 --> 17:21.290
I am your biological daughter.

17:23.720 --> 17:25.160
I will always be grateful

17:25.349 --> 17:27.980
to you two for raising me.

17:28.170 --> 17:29.160
But that doesn't mean

17:29.160 --> 17:30.160
I have to spend my whole life

17:30.160 --> 17:31.880
paying for both of your lives

17:32.750 --> 17:36.090
and bearing
your self-righteous plundering.

18:42.240 --> 18:42.960
[Message]

18:42.980 --> 18:46.140
[Consumer Finance:
Your business loan has been paid with]

18:46.170 --> 18:50.300
[5,000 yuan ahead of time successfully.]
[The payment has been settled this month.]

19:14.450 --> 19:16.130
Are you off work, Ms. Xu?

19:17.330 --> 19:18.130
Get in the car.

19:30.560 --> 19:31.390
Thank you.

19:39.600 --> 19:41.520
Ms. Xu, I'm sorry

19:41.680 --> 19:44.210
for suddenly asking you
to have a meal with me.

19:44.610 --> 19:45.440
It's alright.

19:45.460 --> 19:48.190
Ms. Jiang,
I should thank you for the invitation.

19:48.670 --> 19:50.110
I'm not very good at cooking.

19:50.110 --> 19:52.270
I usually either order takeout

19:52.330 --> 19:54.330
or cook a small pot of rice

19:54.360 --> 19:55.590
and eat it with some side dishes

19:55.590 --> 19:56.920
to grab a bite casually.

19:57.460 --> 19:58.240
Oh, by the way,

19:58.240 --> 19:59.400
let me formally introduce to you

19:59.400 --> 20:00.720
my favorite side dishes for rice.

20:00.720 --> 20:02.830
If you like quick pickles,

20:02.850 --> 20:05.050
you can taste this bowl of sour celtuce.

20:08.010 --> 20:09.160
Is this celtuce?

20:10.670 --> 20:12.290
It's a kind of mixed pickles.

20:12.400 --> 20:14.730
It's a very common brand in supermarkets.

20:15.140 --> 20:17.530
The radish inside is soft,

20:17.550 --> 20:19.040
and the cabbage is a bit too salty.

20:19.040 --> 20:20.280
But only this celtuce

20:20.310 --> 20:21.600
is pickled just right.

20:21.620 --> 20:23.290
It's crisp and sour,

20:23.350 --> 20:25.680
just like a breath of fresh air
in the mess.

20:25.780 --> 20:27.580
Pickles are really amazing.

20:27.600 --> 20:28.770
They don't wait for anyone.

20:28.770 --> 20:31.040
If you eat them at their best time,

20:31.070 --> 20:33.930
it's even more wonderful
than winning the lottery.

20:34.610 --> 20:35.960
At their best time.

20:36.950 --> 20:37.860
Ms. Xu.

20:38.280 --> 20:40.810
You always say things that deeply move me.

20:41.810 --> 20:44.340
Ms. Jiang,
aren't you at your best time now?

20:44.650 --> 20:46.510
Speaking of a person's best time,

20:48.060 --> 20:50.390
perhaps only the person knows it himself.

20:50.720 --> 20:52.920
Maybe it's not the most glorious moment

20:53.140 --> 20:54.660
that outsiders can see.

20:55.210 --> 20:58.790
Nor is it the time
when one is full of hope for the future.

20:58.810 --> 21:01.520
It's not even the time
of financial freedom

21:01.550 --> 21:03.210
or spiritual freedom.

21:03.300 --> 21:04.620
Rather, it's the time

21:05.960 --> 21:08.020
when that very person is by your side.

21:11.960 --> 21:13.290
Ms. Xu.

21:15.880 --> 21:18.210
I asked Mr. Ji
to get back together with me.

21:22.690 --> 21:23.610
Is that so?

21:24.240 --> 21:25.290
What do you think?

21:28.480 --> 21:29.930
I think it's great.

21:30.190 --> 21:31.550
You two are a good match.

21:32.080 --> 21:34.080
Aren't you going to ask if he agreed?

21:36.300 --> 21:39.210
I don't think
this has anything to do with me.

21:43.550 --> 21:44.550
Ms. Xu.

21:44.990 --> 21:46.360
You must have heard

21:46.590 --> 21:49.050
that I've been
having some problems lately.

21:51.570 --> 21:52.970
For a moment,

21:53.350 --> 21:54.960
I even thought

21:55.340 --> 21:57.000
it would be better to just die.

21:57.960 --> 21:58.690
Don't worry.

21:59.070 --> 22:00.160
I'm fine.

22:00.790 --> 22:01.590
Fortunately,

22:01.920 --> 22:04.110
Ji Feng found me in time.

22:04.920 --> 22:06.770
I was so happy at that time.

22:07.070 --> 22:07.790
I felt that

22:08.200 --> 22:09.720
he still cared about me.

22:10.420 --> 22:12.020
Even if that wasn't the case,

22:12.630 --> 22:13.460
I thought

22:14.000 --> 22:15.880
seeing me in such a miserable state,

22:15.880 --> 22:16.480
he would at least

22:16.480 --> 22:18.340
say something nice to comfort me.

22:20.310 --> 22:21.510
Guess what

22:21.790 --> 22:23.190
he said to me at that time?

22:25.250 --> 22:26.210
He said

22:26.880 --> 22:28.540
it was impossible between us.

22:29.610 --> 22:31.090
The person he likes is you.

22:35.550 --> 22:36.720
Even though Ji Feng

22:37.160 --> 22:38.970
is usually quite shrewd

22:39.000 --> 22:40.280
in the workplace,

22:40.990 --> 22:42.250
actually, in his daily life,

22:42.250 --> 22:43.510
he's just that simple.

22:43.830 --> 22:45.960
If he likes someone, he just likes her.

22:46.130 --> 22:48.590
If he doesn't like someone,
he just doesn't.

22:48.640 --> 22:50.320
There is no middle ground.

22:51.530 --> 22:53.920
He brought me back here that day

22:53.940 --> 22:55.260
and left right away.

22:55.470 --> 22:57.470
Hailin was also at home at that time.

22:58.100 --> 23:01.300
Being photographed by reporters
was purely an accident.

23:01.330 --> 23:03.130
I hope you won't misunderstand.

23:07.120 --> 23:08.090
Also,

23:09.820 --> 23:10.780
previously,

23:11.590 --> 23:13.640
after the live stream,

23:13.720 --> 23:15.480
I told you those things

23:16.400 --> 23:17.360
because I actually...

23:17.360 --> 23:19.700
wanted to persuade you to leave Ji Feng.

23:20.550 --> 23:22.260
I acted too despicably.

23:23.160 --> 23:24.540
I owe you an apology.

23:25.960 --> 23:26.770
I'm sorry.

23:28.120 --> 23:28.840
Ms. Jiang.

23:28.860 --> 23:29.650
Miyu.

23:29.920 --> 23:31.050
Don't you think

23:31.970 --> 23:33.830
you owe yourself an apology, too?

23:36.420 --> 23:38.680
You're clearly so nice to everyone else,

23:39.910 --> 23:41.850
but not to yourself.

23:42.440 --> 23:44.030
You hold back your hatred

23:45.110 --> 23:46.710
and even suppress your love.

23:47.850 --> 23:49.710
Don't you think that's too cruel?

23:50.850 --> 23:52.580
Those who truly care about you

23:53.210 --> 23:54.650
and want to love you

23:55.410 --> 23:57.210
don't even know what to do.

23:58.800 --> 23:59.640
Look.

24:01.750 --> 24:03.160
The best time

24:04.400 --> 24:06.360
always slips away quietly.

24:07.640 --> 24:10.880
When I was at my best time,

24:11.240 --> 24:13.170
I failed to grasp the essence of it.

24:13.860 --> 24:16.640
Now that I know the essence of it,

24:17.090 --> 24:19.080
everything has changed.

24:20.160 --> 24:21.450
I'm like this

24:21.750 --> 24:23.440
over-pickled radish,

24:23.830 --> 24:26.230
instead of the perfectly pickled celtuce.

24:26.350 --> 24:27.610
But you are different.

24:29.810 --> 24:31.440
Don't let hesitation

24:32.720 --> 24:34.430
make you miss the right time

24:35.870 --> 24:37.070
and the right person.

24:44.440 --> 24:45.950
I got it, Ms. Jiang.

24:47.780 --> 24:48.960
Thank you.

25:30.090 --> 25:31.620
Time cannot be turned back.

25:32.130 --> 25:34.400
Once a path is taken,

25:34.710 --> 25:35.790
it's just taken.

25:36.770 --> 25:38.970
For example, if those documents
are blown away by the wind,

25:37.000 --> 25:40.630
♪ Love is truly not easy to obtain ♪

25:39.470 --> 25:42.160
what we can catch
can only be the next page.

25:44.380 --> 25:48.110
♪ I can't hold on to you
if you want to leave ♪

25:45.920 --> 25:47.070
This is not fair.

25:48.200 --> 25:49.800
I've clearly become better.

25:49.890 --> 25:50.650
Yes.

25:51.570 --> 25:55.480
♪ I tell myself I'm not hurt
once things settle down ♪

25:51.650 --> 25:53.050
The better Jiang Zhichun

25:53.450 --> 25:54.920
deserves a better future,

25:55.400 --> 25:58.200
instead of being trapped
in the past assumptions.

25:58.980 --> 26:02.790
♪ But I realize I can't deceive myself ♪

25:59.850 --> 26:00.640
Yeah.

26:01.720 --> 26:03.780
I should have understood it earlier.

26:04.280 --> 26:05.280
A businessperson

26:05.770 --> 26:08.160
should solve problems in a business way.

26:06.380 --> 26:10.500
♪ I always say
life is already hard enough ♪

26:08.460 --> 26:09.260
For example?

26:10.530 --> 26:14.700
For example,
if they use cyberbullying as a weapon,

26:14.010 --> 26:18.040
♪ So what else is there worth trying for ♪

26:16.360 --> 26:18.080
I should show them

26:18.800 --> 26:20.670
what a real public opinion war is.

26:21.350 --> 26:25.390
♪ Friends comfort me,
telling me to have a drink ♪

26:22.460 --> 26:23.940
That's more like you.

26:28.640 --> 26:30.160
Let me ask you one last question.

26:28.960 --> 26:32.860
♪ But I've already started living
like I'm not myself anymore ♪

26:36.440 --> 26:39.320
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

26:37.380 --> 26:38.560
For all these years,

26:40.680 --> 26:42.160
have you ever had a moment of...

26:42.160 --> 26:42.990
Yes, I have.

26:42.680 --> 26:48.530
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

26:45.440 --> 26:47.100
But it was exactly those times

26:48.320 --> 26:49.720
that made me more certain

26:50.230 --> 26:52.610
that the best distance between us

26:51.020 --> 26:54.250
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

26:53.720 --> 26:55.060
is just like this now.

26:57.630 --> 27:03.350
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

27:04.530 --> 27:07.390
♪ I've been indulging myself ♪

27:06.890 --> 27:08.420
Thank you for your honesty.

27:21.860 --> 27:24.820
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

27:24.990 --> 27:25.840
This time,

27:28.120 --> 27:33.970
♪ I feel reluctant to recall
or forget those memories ♪

27:28.610 --> 27:30.410
it's really time to say goodbye.

27:36.370 --> 27:40.380
♪ I feel reluctant ♪

27:39.740 --> 27:40.980
Ms. Xu.

27:41.800 --> 27:43.410
Love is troublesome,

27:42.200 --> 27:47.960
♪ I feel reluctant to grab on to anyone
and I can't breathe ♪

27:44.030 --> 27:46.100
but it's worth our courage.

27:49.710 --> 27:52.230
♪ I've cut myself some slack ♪

27:52.130 --> 27:58.630
[Purong Hotel Staff Apartment]

28:10.400 --> 28:11.250
Hello.

28:11.510 --> 28:12.270
Ji Feng.

28:12.860 --> 28:13.910
Where are you?

28:14.090 --> 28:14.890
Where are you?

28:15.390 --> 28:17.390
I'm on my way to the hotel to find you.

28:18.070 --> 28:19.800
I-I have something to tell you.

28:19.920 --> 28:21.170
I'm downstairs at your dorm.

28:21.170 --> 28:22.050
Wait for me.

28:38.070 --> 28:39.850
-I have something to tell you.
-I have something to tell you.

28:39.850 --> 28:40.950
Let me say it first.

28:41.550 --> 28:42.260
Okay.

28:42.280 --> 28:43.240
I admit

28:43.940 --> 28:46.200
in terms of starting a new relationship,

28:46.550 --> 28:47.930
now I'm a bit afraid

28:47.990 --> 28:49.200
and reserved.

28:50.140 --> 28:52.070
I have let myself down for too long.

28:52.080 --> 28:53.230
Right now,

28:53.480 --> 28:56.290
I just want to give all my love
and expectations back to myself.

28:56.290 --> 28:57.300
I am very afraid.

28:57.690 --> 29:00.350
I'm afraid that if I fall in love
with someone again,

29:00.350 --> 29:02.080
I will repeat my past mistakes,

29:02.820 --> 29:05.450
so I've been
looking for all kinds of excuses

29:05.480 --> 29:07.280
to avoid my feelings for you.

29:07.920 --> 29:09.160
But now,

29:10.020 --> 29:11.090
I don't want to

29:11.570 --> 29:13.450
and I can't avoid them anymore.

29:16.020 --> 29:16.820
Ji Feng.

29:18.690 --> 29:20.130
I want to start over

29:21.830 --> 29:22.510
with you.

29:43.990 --> 29:45.920
I'm glad I'm with you finally.

29:46.740 --> 29:48.780
I've also always wanted to tell you

29:49.550 --> 29:51.000
I like you too.

30:38.890 --> 30:41.870
♪ Bury everything in your mind ♪

30:42.880 --> 30:45.730
♪ Hope love blossoms as wished ♪

30:46.470 --> 30:50.040
♪ Rainwater silently nourishes flowers ♪

30:51.280 --> 30:52.380
♪ At its own expense ♪

30:53.220 --> 30:55.400
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

30:56.250 --> 30:59.200
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

31:00.220 --> 31:03.140
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

31:03.880 --> 31:06.940
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

31:08.130 --> 31:10.330
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

31:11.210 --> 31:14.020
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

31:15.050 --> 31:18.130
♪ Questions without answers ♪

31:19.110 --> 31:21.760
♪ Let them go with the wind ♪

31:23.220 --> 31:24.760
♪ Let them go ♪

31:35.280 --> 31:36.140
Morning.

31:36.360 --> 31:37.070
Morning.

31:46.510 --> 31:47.510
Wait.

31:48.320 --> 31:50.890
I don't want to
bring personal feelings into work.

31:50.890 --> 31:52.700
You're still Mr. Ji, the general manager,

31:52.700 --> 31:54.230
and I'm Ms. Xu, the manager.

31:54.230 --> 31:55.960
We're both very professional.

31:59.640 --> 32:00.360
Thank you.

32:02.480 --> 32:05.170
Then let's just talk about business.

32:06.120 --> 32:08.040
You said you wanted to transfer
to the sales department.

32:08.040 --> 32:09.900
Can you give me a specific reason?

32:12.770 --> 32:13.880
I think,

32:13.900 --> 32:16.940
from the jazz performance
at the Western Restaurant last time

32:16.940 --> 32:19.480
to the planning
of the college entrance exam rooms,

32:19.480 --> 32:22.130
I do have some talent for sales.

32:23.540 --> 32:26.280
You do have sales intuition
and execution ability.

32:26.280 --> 32:27.680
But competing with those

32:27.750 --> 32:30.750
top sales reps
who specialize in developing business

32:30.850 --> 32:31.990
is a different thing.

32:31.990 --> 32:32.550
Besides,

32:32.950 --> 32:33.670
sales is

32:33.690 --> 32:35.270
also completely different from

32:35.270 --> 32:36.870
the work you've done before.

32:36.890 --> 32:39.290
As for the methods and tactics
it requires,

32:39.590 --> 32:40.640
are you able to use them?

32:40.640 --> 32:41.830
Everyone is different.

32:41.830 --> 32:43.100
A thousand people have a thousand faces.

32:43.100 --> 32:45.470
I don't think I might be able to be

32:45.510 --> 32:48.160
that kind of aggressive sales rep
who people can't refuse,

32:48.160 --> 32:51.370
but I can understand the products

32:51.390 --> 32:52.730
and learn about the clients,

32:52.730 --> 32:55.430
trying to facilitate a mutual choice
between them.

32:55.430 --> 32:56.250
Well,

32:56.500 --> 32:57.480
what about Lu Zhenzhen?

32:57.480 --> 32:58.880
Her maternity leave is almost over.

32:58.880 --> 33:00.110
How will you deal with her
when she returns?

33:00.110 --> 33:02.160
I've never thought about
how to deal with her.

33:02.160 --> 33:03.570
She's not in my plan.

33:03.740 --> 33:05.550
I have my own mountain to climb.

33:06.210 --> 33:07.220
Okay.

33:08.390 --> 33:11.000
I used to think the hotel industry

33:11.020 --> 33:12.550
was just a

33:12.790 --> 33:13.990
temporary job for me.

33:14.370 --> 33:16.000
I had no career plan.

33:16.170 --> 33:17.500
But it's different now.

33:17.650 --> 33:19.540
My current goal is

33:19.560 --> 33:21.820
to become a professional hotel manager.

33:24.480 --> 33:25.200
Alright.

33:26.290 --> 33:27.940
Then you have to think it through.

33:27.940 --> 33:28.910
If you join the sales department now,

33:28.910 --> 33:31.530
you'll need to start
as an ordinary employee

33:31.760 --> 33:32.620
with a demotion

33:32.630 --> 33:33.760
and a post transfer.

33:34.580 --> 33:35.640
Do you understand?

33:36.770 --> 33:37.570
Yes, I do.

33:40.080 --> 33:40.840
Come in.

33:42.480 --> 33:43.050
Mr. Ji.

33:43.310 --> 33:44.440
Mr. Wei is here.

33:45.340 --> 33:46.340
Mr. Ji.

33:46.850 --> 33:49.110
I was just passing by,
so I came to see you.

33:55.780 --> 33:57.130
Am I disturbing you?

33:59.490 --> 34:00.430
No, not at all.

34:02.930 --> 34:05.320
What can I do for you, Mr. Wei?

34:05.800 --> 34:08.130
There's no need to be so formal
between us.

34:08.889 --> 34:11.030
I heard some gossip about you.

34:11.230 --> 34:11.820
Have a seat.

34:11.820 --> 34:12.969
Let's talk. Come on.

34:18.739 --> 34:21.330
I've recently heard people in the hotel
gossiping about you.

34:21.330 --> 34:21.920
They say you

34:21.920 --> 34:23.880
and Xu Miyu,
the Front Office's lobby manager,

34:23.880 --> 34:25.610
have an unusual relationship.

34:31.280 --> 34:32.340
Actually, I understand.

34:32.340 --> 34:33.370
As a boss,

34:33.400 --> 34:36.060
it's normal
to have a few capable subordinates.

34:36.420 --> 34:39.500
But Xu Miyu seems a bit different.

34:40.920 --> 34:41.900
Look. I remember that

34:41.900 --> 34:43.840
shortly after she started
working in our hotel,

34:43.840 --> 34:45.350
she joined the management team.

34:45.350 --> 34:47.260
Now she's suddenly being transferred
to the sales department.

34:47.260 --> 34:49.449
Her speed is a bit fast.

34:49.860 --> 34:52.260
It's inevitable that people would gossip.

34:52.280 --> 34:53.590
As a housewife

34:53.610 --> 34:55.080
who had never worked before,

34:55.080 --> 34:56.060
she joined Purong Hotel

34:56.060 --> 34:57.190
and then suddenly became

34:57.190 --> 34:58.440
an influential figure.

34:58.440 --> 34:59.920
Not to mention everyone else,

34:59.920 --> 35:01.780
even I don't quite understand it.

35:03.020 --> 35:03.870
Mr. Ji,

35:04.450 --> 35:06.980
do you know
what the subordinates are saying?

35:07.950 --> 35:10.070
Ten years of hard work at Purong Hotel

35:10.090 --> 35:12.680
is not as good as
a glance of favor from Mr. Ji.

35:15.180 --> 35:17.010
Mr. Wei, I'm flattered.

35:17.530 --> 35:19.860
How would I have such great capabilities?

35:20.710 --> 35:21.800
As for how Xu Miyu

35:21.800 --> 35:24.380
became the forewoman
of the executive floor,

35:24.880 --> 35:27.480
I guess no one knows it
better than you, Mr. Wei.

35:31.460 --> 35:32.460
Is that so?

35:34.240 --> 35:35.480
How come I don't remember?

35:35.480 --> 35:37.480
I must be getting old and forgetful.

35:39.010 --> 35:39.970
Perhaps

35:40.210 --> 35:42.160
you've played the role
of talent spotter too many times.

35:42.160 --> 35:43.580
You're teasing me again.

35:45.470 --> 35:47.830
But since Xu Miyu
joined the management team,

35:47.830 --> 35:49.320
everything she did

35:49.350 --> 35:51.150
has been worthy of her position.

35:51.340 --> 35:53.940
Some even exceeded
everyone's expectations.

35:54.190 --> 35:56.230
And now she has been transferred
to the sales department.

35:56.230 --> 35:57.090
It's also because

35:57.090 --> 35:59.090
she has shown ability in this field.

35:59.680 --> 36:02.280
Therefore,
her career path is a natural progression,

36:02.280 --> 36:04.000
and it has nothing to do with me.

36:04.000 --> 36:06.130
However, if there is any controversy,

36:06.200 --> 36:09.400
your criticism and guidance
are always welcome, Mr. Wei.

36:10.730 --> 36:11.920
Mr. Ji,

36:11.940 --> 36:14.280
now that you're saying this,
I understand completely.

36:14.280 --> 36:15.750
There must be some subordinates

36:15.750 --> 36:17.280
who don't understand the situation.

36:17.280 --> 36:18.990
And with people's jealousy,

36:19.010 --> 36:21.280
it's inevitable
that there's some unpleasant gossip.

36:21.280 --> 36:22.940
Please don't take it to heart.

36:23.770 --> 36:26.230
Mr. Ji, speaking of
your dedication to nurturing elites,

36:26.230 --> 36:27.140
I deeply admire it

36:27.140 --> 36:28.740
and can truly understand it.

36:30.230 --> 36:31.310
However,

36:33.560 --> 36:35.210
I think when it comes to eating,

36:35.210 --> 36:37.410
you still need to take one bite at a time.

36:37.520 --> 36:39.850
Don't pull up seedlings to help them grow.

36:40.670 --> 36:43.130
Losing your favorite aide
is a small matter,

36:43.550 --> 36:45.320
but ruining the hotel's development

36:45.320 --> 36:46.780
would outweigh the gains.

36:47.360 --> 36:48.030
Am I right?

36:58.070 --> 36:58.950
Mr. Wei,

36:59.720 --> 37:00.680
you're right.

37:00.710 --> 37:01.940
I've learned a lot.

37:06.480 --> 37:07.960
I wouldn't dare to teach you anything.

37:07.960 --> 37:10.010
Mr. Ji, you've seen a lot
of the world outside.

37:10.010 --> 37:12.340
I'm just showing off
in front of an expert.

37:13.140 --> 37:15.270
But I still want to ask about one thing.

37:15.430 --> 37:16.840
As for Xu Miyu's specific

37:17.070 --> 37:19.000
work arrangements in the sales department,

37:19.000 --> 37:20.870
will you have any special...

37:20.900 --> 37:22.290
There are no special arrangements.

37:22.290 --> 37:25.350
Do everything in accordance
with the sales department's rules.

37:25.350 --> 37:26.150
Got it.

37:26.850 --> 37:28.200
It means she should do what she has to do.

37:28.200 --> 37:28.950
Right.

37:29.950 --> 37:30.830
In that case, I am a bit

37:30.830 --> 37:33.160
looking forward to her work performance.

37:33.770 --> 37:34.400
Mr. Ji,

37:34.610 --> 37:36.610
I won't take up any more of your time.

37:38.130 --> 37:39.480
No need to see me out.

37:39.510 --> 37:40.250
Goodbye.

37:40.280 --> 37:41.030
Alright.

37:47.300 --> 37:48.100
Mr. Lin.

37:51.800 --> 37:52.630
Xu Miyu.

37:53.510 --> 37:54.860
So you're transferred
from the Front Office?

37:54.860 --> 37:55.430
Yes.

37:55.810 --> 37:56.820
So you've had no experience in this field?

37:56.820 --> 37:57.680
No.

37:58.830 --> 37:59.410
Alright.

38:15.420 --> 38:16.680
Make some phone calls.

38:17.150 --> 38:18.670
You want me to make phone calls?

38:18.670 --> 38:19.600
Telemarketing.

38:19.810 --> 38:20.940
You can do that, huh?

38:24.840 --> 38:29.130
[List of Potential Clients]

38:30.790 --> 38:32.090
[Call]

38:33.100 --> 38:33.560
Hello.

38:33.600 --> 38:36.290
Is that Jingkun Travel Company?

38:37.130 --> 38:38.000
This is...

38:42.490 --> 38:42.990
[Shanghai Experimental Exploration
Food Company]

38:43.010 --> 38:43.610
[Shanghai Life Ark
Medical Supplies Company]

38:46.670 --> 38:47.350
Hello.

38:47.380 --> 38:48.050
Hello.

38:48.870 --> 38:51.400
This is Xu Miyu,
a sales rep from Purong Hotel.

38:51.400 --> 38:53.240
What business would you like to handle?

38:53.240 --> 38:55.000
No, I just want to ask whether you

38:55.000 --> 38:57.420
have any need for hotel services.

38:57.440 --> 38:58.290
No.

38:58.350 --> 38:59.620
[Shanghai Kangyu Future
Textile Technology Company]

38:59.690 --> 39:00.690
Hello.

39:01.510 --> 39:03.030
Hello, this is...

39:03.380 --> 39:03.800
[Shanghai Polaris Ship Hotspot Company]

39:03.820 --> 39:04.440
[Shanghai Sunlight Epoch
Renewable Energy Company]

39:04.820 --> 39:05.240
[Call]

39:06.070 --> 39:07.550
Hello, this is...

39:08.030 --> 39:09.110
Hello.

39:09.960 --> 39:10.590
Hello.

39:10.590 --> 39:14.110
This is Purong Hotel's...

39:14.510 --> 39:15.320
[Shanghai Genetic Blueprint Company]

39:15.350 --> 39:16.460
[Shanghai Recycle and Regeneration
Chemical Company]

39:16.480 --> 39:18.790
[Shanghai Golden Stone
Mining & Thermoelectricity Company]

39:22.980 --> 39:23.590
Hello.

39:23.590 --> 39:25.540
Is that Rongfei Trading Company?

39:25.560 --> 39:27.460
Yes. What's the matter?

39:28.080 --> 39:30.610
This is Xu Miyu,
a sales rep from Purong Hotel.

39:30.630 --> 39:31.590
I'd like to ask whether you

39:31.590 --> 39:33.920
have any need for hotel services.

39:33.920 --> 39:35.450
We can discuss the details.

39:35.470 --> 39:36.400
Purong, right?

39:36.430 --> 39:37.280
Yes.

39:37.700 --> 39:39.700
Send us some info. We'll take a look.

39:39.850 --> 39:41.880
Okay. I'll add you on WeChat right now.

39:41.880 --> 39:42.480
Alright.

39:42.810 --> 39:44.000
Thank you.

39:53.050 --> 39:54.220
Good job, Xu.

39:54.920 --> 39:56.800
It's all thanks to
your good guidance, Mr. Lin.

39:56.800 --> 39:59.240
By the way, when will you be available?

39:59.270 --> 40:01.130
They want to talk to you directly.

40:01.540 --> 40:02.100
No need.

40:02.400 --> 40:04.530
I won't meet with such small potatoes.

40:05.380 --> 40:08.580
No matter how small the business is,
it's still business.

40:09.390 --> 40:11.860
The smaller the business is,
the less reliable it might be.

40:11.860 --> 40:13.420
We'd rather miss it

40:13.840 --> 40:15.110
than take the risk.

40:15.130 --> 40:16.190
Do you understand?

40:16.830 --> 40:17.820
But...

40:18.210 --> 40:20.670
The scale of this company
may be small now.

40:20.700 --> 40:23.070
What if it grows bigger in the future?

40:23.660 --> 40:26.120
I've seen too many tricks
from such small companies.

40:26.120 --> 40:27.400
If they could sign a contract with you,

40:27.400 --> 40:28.770
why didn't they just sign it?

40:28.770 --> 40:30.580
They just want to come here
for free food and drinks.

40:30.580 --> 40:32.180
That's how telemarketing is like.

40:32.180 --> 40:33.510
The success rate is low.

40:33.590 --> 40:34.840
It's mainly to train you newcomers

40:34.840 --> 40:36.360
so that you guys can open your mouths,
step forward

40:36.360 --> 40:37.720
and unleash your true nature.

40:37.720 --> 40:38.720
Also, Xu,

40:38.740 --> 40:40.010
our department

40:40.090 --> 40:42.150
doesn't expect you to bring in sales.

40:42.770 --> 40:43.900
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

40:43.900 --> 40:44.660
Okay?

40:45.960 --> 40:47.060
Thank you, Mr. Lin.

40:47.240 --> 40:48.840
I'll think about it further.

40:48.930 --> 40:49.530
Keep it up.
